{"prompt": "Generate a website for a local artist portfolio. The website should be secure and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Artist Portfolio</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #8B0000; /* Dark Red */\n            --secondary-color: #A9A9A9; /* Dark Grey */\n            --text-color: #FFFFFF;\n            --background-color: #1a1a1a;\n        }\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            background: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n        #hero {\n            min-height: 400px;\n            background: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x400/8B0000/FFFFFF?text=Artist+Gallery') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        #hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n        #hero .hero-content {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            letter-spacing: 3px;\n        }\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            font-weight: lighter;\n        }\n        #portfolio .portfolio-items {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        .portfolio-item {\n            background: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 15px;\n            text-align: center;\n            border: 2px solid var(--primary-color);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .portfolio-item img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            border: 2px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n        .portfolio-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n        .portfolio-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n        #about, #contact {\n            padding: 50px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        #about h2, #contact h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        #contact form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n        #contact label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        #contact input[type=\"text\"],\n        #contact input[type=\"email\"],\n        #contact textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            background: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n        #contact button {\n            display: block;\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 10px;\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            border: none;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        #contact button:hover {\n            background: #a00000; /* Slightly lighter red */\n        }\n        footer {\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            border-top: 2px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n        .secure-indicator {\n            font-size: 0.8em;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            opacity: 0.7;\n            padding: 5px 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>[Artist Name]</h1>\n        <p>Creative Visions</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <a href=\"#hero\">Home</a>\n            <a href=\"#portfolio\">Portfolio</a>\n            <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"hero-content\">\n            <h2>Artistry Unveiled</h2>\n            <p>Exploring the Spectrum of Imagination</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"portfolio\">\n            <h2>Portfolio Highlights</h2>\n            <div class=\"portfolio-items\">\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/8B0000/FFFFFF?text=Artwork+1\" alt=\"Artwork 1\">\n                    <h3>Abstract Serenity</h3>\n                    <p>A vibrant exploration of form and color.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/8B0000/FFFFFF?text=Artwork+2\" alt=\"Artwork 2\">\n                    <h3>Urban Echoes</h3>\n                    <p>Capturing the essence of city life.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/8B0000/FFFFFF?text=Artwork+3\" alt=\"Artwork 3\">\n                    <h3>Nature's Embrace</h3>\n                    <p>Inspired by the tranquility of the natural world.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/8B0000/FFFFFF?text=Artwork+4\" alt=\"Artwork 4\">\n                    <h3>Figurative Study</h3>\n                    <p>A deeper look into human form and emotion.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About the Artist</h2>\n            <p>\n                [Artist Name] is a contemporary artist known for their [mention style, e.g., bold use of color, intricate detail, abstract expressionism].\n                With a passion for [mention inspiration, e.g., storytelling, human connection, the natural world],\n                each piece aims to evoke a sense of [mention feeling, e.g., wonder, introspection, joy].\n                Explore the collection and discover a world of artistic expression.\n            </p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>For inquiries, commissions, or just to say hello, please use the form below.</p>\n            <form id=\"contact-form\">\n                <label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"email\">Email:</label>\n                <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"message\">Message:</label>\n                <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" rows=\"5\" required></textarea>\n\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n            <div class=\"secure-indicator\">\n                <p>This is a secure connection.</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 [Artist Name]. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.getElementById('contact-form').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            alert('Message sent! Thank you for your interest.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>"}